summary:
This Mod will enable you to fasttravel from anywhere. Normally you\'d have to find your own Way out of a dark Cave, now you can just fasttravel out of there.
WARNING: If a Script from a Quest depends on you being there for a While because you\'re normally not able to fasttravel away, this Mod may screw with your Game.
descriptionHtml:
This Mod will give you the Ability to fasttravel out of any indoor Location, including every Shop, every Dungeon and every Cave.
Warning: If a Script depends on you not fasttraveling from somewhere, this mod may screw with your Game. When some NPC removes your Weapons before going somewhere, you may lose your Weapons when you fasttravel away.

This Mod will make it possible to get out of a Cave fully packed with Loot without having to find your own Way out. Have Fun!
author: Madman123456
